{"tid":1202644,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"［I/A］Durango：野生之地（1）超高自由度mmorpg","createTime":"2019-06-11T09:54:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T18:31:46.000Z","uid":111497,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"139ae3519beac899120978bd6d5bfe3000884fb2","tid":1202644,"uid":111497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:54:37.000Z","msg":"《Durango》是一款生存拓荒類型的手機遊戲，故事背景是現代人玩家搭乘列車因為發生意外捲入時空的扭曲，意外穿越了有恐龍的原始世界，遊戲最大特色就是可以不用再只是透過戰鬥來生存，也能夠選擇依靠料理、製作、採集等方式在這個世界中生存下去。<br />\n官網: <a href=\"https://durango.nexon.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdurango.nexon.com%2F&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAo6QEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=f6ebce58\" target=\"_blank\">https://durango.nexon.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n遊戲圖片：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fPS6HrB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfPS6HrB.jpg&h=9b912702&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ndnnfMC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FndnnfMC.jpg&h=4b4589f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NNr7rTh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNNr7rTh.jpg&h=8fdb3497&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nPTJKEY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnPTJKEY.jpg&h=a8de2bea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SrvW4EY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSrvW4EY.jpg&h=f1faf305&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ddTxCZZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FddTxCZZ.jpg&h=230e4ea2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C1VW4E0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC1VW4E0.jpg&h=409a5264&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲影片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1513780142253708/posts/2143561272608922?s=1253660627&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1513780142253708%2Fposts%2F2143561272608922%3Fs%3D1253660627%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAo6QEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=1f9c69c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1513780142253708/posts/2143561272608922?s=1253660627&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n野生Q&amp;A:<br />\nQ: 一開波我應該揀咩職業?<br />\nA: 每個職業技能上限等級係Lv60, 前期揀咩職業都無所謂, 純粹一開波果一項職業技能Lv20, 但當你玩玩下覺得唔想玩其他技能, 每日有5點技能點比你重置<br />\n<br />\nQ: 咩係個人島、城市島同不法島?<br />\nA: 一開始玩家會有一個個人島, 傢俱/工具所有野都唔會扣耐久度, 但與世隔絕；城市島Lv40就可以我到, 同一個島Share咁多個玩家同公會, 所以揀地果陣小心格黎擴充領地, 擴到你無位, 而城市島領地每日都要比維修費, 所以建議你地入Lihkg1會/2會/三五成群錢公會, 咁樣就可以慳番筆錢, 又可以同其他玩家互動, 各取所需；而不法島就要Lv60先去到, 簡單D講就係Pvp島<br />\n<br />\nQ: 我應唔應該課金? 課左金要買乜?<br />\nA: 單機就唔建議課金, 入左公會先課金先可以炫富架麻!課金可以選擇買寵物, 例如: 拉布拉多、大笨象, 另外想快速上60就可以買快速成長禮包, 同埋可以買傢俱, 因為課金既傢俱真心好屈機（快速回能量同快速減疲勞度）<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點升Lv最快?<br />\nA: 做任務, 瘋狂做任務. 搵唔到就係市場搵平貨交任, 等30mins又再做, 咁樣好快60lv. 如果想知技能點升最快可以參考巴哈狗既Post<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=26406&amp;snA=643\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D26406%26snA%3D643&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAo6QEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=ace7bb13\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=26406&amp;snA=643</a>"},{"pid":"1a317a288cfe2978567093cfaa6df5b57ff160c3","tid":1202644,"uid":111497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:04:43.000Z","msg":"玩嘅記住係Asia II"},{"pid":"43889894febb554196f3b8fe99ee12a6e7f7a65d","tid":1202644,"uid":111497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:48:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed661df1f81eaf1cfcba876055d54482e1b80dc","tid":1202644,"uid":111497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /